sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Internet User
    participant IGW as Internet Gateway
    participant ALB as Public ALB
    participant APP as Private App Server
    participant DB as Isolated Database
    participant NAT as NAT Gateway
    participant AWS as AWS Services

    User->>IGW: HTTPS request
    IGW->>ALB: Forward to ALB
    ALB->>APP: App traffic on approved port
    APP->>DB: Database traffic on approved port
    APP->>NAT: Outbound updates/API calls
    NAT->>AWS: Internet or AWS public endpoint path
    APP->>AWS: Private access through VPC Endpoint where configured
    DB--xInternet User: No direct internet route
